Squizzy::

She ran and didn't realize she was even headed for the Alliance 
ship.  She just ran.  She found her crossbow still on her hip.  She 
stopped, loaded it and fired one bolt at the bot flying after her.  
She then reloaded it, turned and ran, still headed towards the ship.
"Please, leave me alone." as she ran, panicked and not thinking.
